{"tid":60954,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"講到尾 籃球同足球都一樣係玩具","createTime":"2016-12-30T22:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T03:52:46.000Z","uid":35584,"like":66,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90509b4041567393ed4ffd696a2dc2091b6ae60e","tid":60954,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T22:38:13.000Z","msg":"排球先係真男人玩既球類活動<br />\n<br />\n1.團隊性<br />\n籃球你勁既你可以一過五再入樽<br />\n足球你勁既你可以一扭十一直接帶波入籠<br />\n但係排球有三傳 你唔可以一個人打曬三傳<br />\n就算一傳過網都做唔到有威脅既攻勢<br />\n一個james都可以打贏一隊中學生<br />\n一個美斯都可以踢贏一隊中學生<br />\n但係一個世界級排球選手都唔會打得贏一隊中學生<br />\n<br />\n2.基本功<br />\n猜下手上手 唔好話猜得靚 <br />\n練到玩到呢樣運動都起碼要半年至一年時間<br />\n籃球我三歲都已經識左右手拍波<br />\n足球我幼稚園都已經搞緊比賽 仲比老師吹我手球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比你班籃足球撚打球下手個波都唔知去撚左邊<br />\n<br />\n3.受傷機會<br />\n排球下下救波都要訓落地 魚躍側滾樣樣齊<br />\n室內場都還好 係學校練波石地黎架<br />\n每個排球撚兩邊盤骨位膝頭手掙都肯定有損過既印 呢d先係真男人<br />\n籃球撚掂一掂就foul<br />\n足球撚插個水就有十二碼<br />\n排球一場都要訓過百次地<br />\n仆撚死都未必有分攞<br />\n比你班籃足撚 係冬天猜個下手都要搵媽媽抱<br />\n<br />\n4.戰術<br />\n排球每一個來回球都要比戰術<br />\n一個位置都起碼記十幾種戰術<br />\n籃足撚咪又係教練講乜你做乜<br />\n但係排球戰術全部都要係來回球一秒間比出 全部球員自己思考 <br />\n而唔係籃足撚成個小朋友咁聽教聽話<br />\n<br />\n5.體能要求<br />\n排球大部分動作都要跳<br />\n開波要跳 set波jump set  快攻要跳fake人 鎚手要跳 攔網要跳<br />\n一個三傳攔網手都要跳兩野<br />\n一場波都跳成三四百下<br />\n而且高度既集中力會令個人好攰<br />\n殺波/比人攔網熄燈 個波跟本快到睇唔到<br />\n全部都要靠準備同集中力<br />\n籃球撚就成日time out 換人抖<br />\n足球撚就成日行行企企事不關己<br />\n排球跟本冇時間比你hea<br />\n得分慶祝完就要諗戰術<br />\n失分就要集中接發球<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.觀賞性<br />\n排球係比分制 而唔係時間制 <br />\n唔會有冷場<br />\n籃球又有24秒 多罰球又悶 又成日time out<br />\n足球仲衰 90分鐘可能得幾次攻門<br />\n排球一分係幾秒之間既事<br />\n可能你波都未睇到就完左<br />\n節奏緊湊過籃足撚好多<br />\n<br />\n7.普及性<br />\n排球既普及性遠低於籃足撚<br />\n因為排球既難度高好多<br />\n唔似籃足球兩歲細路都識玩 甚至連狗都玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會有籃球機啊？因為籃球係玩具<br />\n咁點解會有足球機啊？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為足球都係玩具囉</span><br />\n有冇見過排球有玩具比細路比狗玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多唔多得過籃足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結論係 如果籃球係玩具 足球又何嘗唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n足球撚硬係要計既話 跟本籃足都係玩具<br />\n排球先係男人打既波<br />\n排球殺落低既聲先係力的表現<br />\n救波落地既動作先係不放棄不認輸既決心<br />\n攔網熄人燈先係最霸氣既王者姿態<br />\nsetter先係中場指揮官 默默付出既好男人<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"8a5c22fde008c6bcc9f7f540b584127f7836f6fe","tid":60954,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T22:44:27.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"6f227d70d822fabc60bca4f97a2cd2dc263303f9","tid":60954,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T22:45:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acbdffc681e455868dbb696c71ea0ff794ec2a9d","tid":60954,"uid":69057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T22:52:21.000Z","msg":"而且排球唔知點解好多女玩"},{"pid":"f28ffefef27d7082d94edcdc7889287f2abd887c","tid":60954,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T22:54:42.000Z","msg":"你同波台班傻閪講咁多道理都無用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b80611b81d67f40b0e3e654c421a2e1bcce962","tid":60954,"uid":62092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T22:58:15.000Z","msg":"男排就係太快所以冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6068322ec7f31724a8e13488f63eb60eeafd33","tid":60954,"uid":16892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T22:59:56.000Z","msg":"死gay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0364a1dc033db27ffcb811e3769768f38c091680","tid":60954,"uid":70028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:06:14.000Z","msg":"唔識駁"},{"pid":"0f15d1f58aa9ad0151278b8da75165e8ee6a7688","tid":60954,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:16:38.000Z","msg":"睇怕樓主對足球既認識仲停留係幼稚園階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9c5ffabc11135d1a020b762e7d3066dbae4163","tid":60954,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T00:14:53.000Z","msg":"人妖先玩排球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e866d7461caf7cf6b1f397666af40511c4d91dcc","tid":60954,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T00:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇怕樓主對足球既認識仲停留係幼稚園階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes 佢真吾識波"},{"pid":"c810a714c407bdda596724df226ae0a5d9ae5417","tid":60954,"uid":22638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T00:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e4524c7c9a0f1fbd238eaf846ea3408ae5b33e","tid":60954,"uid":8988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:42:42.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14a8b4f46a817d27ddbde574669e2879c6ab25e","tid":60954,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:53:19.000Z","msg":"排球只系冇揸球拍既 桌球／羽毛球／網球"},{"pid":"95c00cd023ee4e1d58dd42b87464df16066231ae","tid":60954,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:55:54.000Z","msg":"人妖先打排波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948ba92729c320446899838039f0343a29009cbc","tid":60954,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"ching 講得好<br />\n<br />\n希望班足球藍波撚一齊去玩具台"},{"pid":"a83dd5bd3a8c4ed6c0582f2df4fe3be1effa8e1e","tid":60954,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching ho ball</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9ef36cd93943b504cfeb6e09bcf9a928c655eb81","tid":60954,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7965ad2e0f6b3c080842aa5882e413db9405ca4d","tid":60954,"uid":11173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"結論：藍波贏"},{"pid":"f4b33399d510d4cee76d25ab568a3d2df42d8884","tid":60954,"uid":10625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T03:16:37.000Z","msg":"講得好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 籃排足都有玩"},{"pid":"26c0bb9c495b6af5a1fe128213bf508eeff6dfd4","tid":60954,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人妖先打排波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱阿 人妖先打排球<br />\n矮撚先會踢波"},{"pid":"5883e17caaae29df3b4dd2099cdaaba179d83b80","tid":60954,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>排球只系冇揸球拍既 桌球／羽毛球／網球</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n足球只係係地下玩既桌球/籃球<br />\n同比bb玩既玩具<br />\nbtw系你老母"},{"pid":"d6841ff76b064ed13ec65cf5df550fa40b0af32a","tid":60954,"uid":35584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇怕樓主對足球既認識仲停留係幼稚園階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇怕波台對其他波既認識仲停留係幼稚園階段"},{"pid":"17f446f95d5c5c23b24840fa5359cd768a674efb","tid":60954,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:41:13.000Z","msg":"淨係識屌籃球撚攞優越感<br />\n依家比排球撚屌就搏唔到潛曬水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲係到搞公投玩多數人的暴政<br />\n不知廉恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f42924a9c6c55765e847f3db7e30d326e25b0f4","tid":60954,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:55:04.000Z","msg":"講真要嘈既<br />\n你講個啲大部分都係唔識足球先講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講體能受傷機會團隊性戰術都睇得出你唔識波拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係計彈跳唔計跑動距離呢啲足球最辛苦既野 連下下企企都講得出<br />\n受傷機會呢啲足籃球都要正面同對手有身體踫撞 比起你排球落地而傷既機會大好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講梗你全速比人踢低已經可以好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講戰術含量更加得啖笑<br />\n足球員係場上面對既情況千變萬化 冇可能可以冇即時判斷能力 教練指示一定唔會包得哂你要做既決定<br />\n諗下啲判斷能力差既球員俾人屌得幾勁就知即時判斷幾重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主你真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"c401cdd449df8ff334d2f9315b221069af5bf94f","tid":60954,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真要嘈既<br />\n你講個啲大部分都係唔識足球先講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講體能受傷機會團隊性戰術都睇得出你唔識波拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係計彈跳唔計跑動距離呢啲足球最辛苦既野 連下下企企都講得出<br />\n受傷機會呢啲足籃球都要正面同對手有身體踫撞 比起你排球落地而傷既機會大好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講梗你全速比人踢低已經可以好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講戰術含量更加得啖笑<br />\n足球員係場上面對既情況千變萬化 冇可能可以冇即時判斷能力 教練指示一定唔會包得哂你要做既決定<br />\n諗下啲判斷能力差既球員俾人屌得幾勁就知即時判斷幾重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主你真係得啖笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地夠淨係計跑動距離唔計彈跳呢啲籃球最辛苦既野啦<br />\n乜你地都知籃球都有身體踫撞架咩<br />\n唔係掂下手仔就foul咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n足球撚咪又係拎足球最辛苦既野黎盲撐足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講到尾 如果籃球係玩具既話 足球又何嘗唔係？</span></span>"},{"pid":"b4a0a7468f84f504e04111e8d662345d29b6ac4d","tid":60954,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T19:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真要嘈既<br />\n你講個啲大部分都係唔識足球先講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講體能受傷機會團隊性戰術都睇得出你唔識波拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係計彈跳唔計跑動距離呢啲足球最辛苦既野 連下下企企都講得出<br />\n受傷機會呢啲足籃球都要正面同對手有身體踫撞 比起你排球落地而傷既機會大好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講梗你全速比人踢低已經可以好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講戰術含量更加得啖笑<br />\n足球員係場上面對既情況千變萬化 冇可能可以冇即時判斷能力 教練指示一定唔會包得哂你要做既決定<br />\n諗下啲判斷能力差既球員俾人屌得幾勁就知即時判斷幾重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主你真係得啖笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你地夠淨係計跑動距離唔計彈跳呢啲籃球最辛苦既野啦<br />\n乜你地都知籃球都有身體踫撞架咩<br />\n唔係掂下手仔就foul咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n足球撚咪又係拎足球最辛苦既野黎盲撐足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講到尾 如果籃球係玩具既話 足球又何嘗唔係？</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有數據證明都盲撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直以為你係嘈梗排球先係運動反足籃波原來又係籃波撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我成篇野係駁你足球比唔上排球既論點<br />\n點知你九唔撘八又應啲唔應啲<br />\n咁即係你想借足球撚平反你講既野黎撐籃波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係既真係辛苦哂你打篇垃圾出黎俾人駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj